<h1><%= @heartfelts.name %></h1>
<br>
<h4><%= @heartfelts.description%></h4>
<br>
<h4>Why will I enjoy this activity?</h4>
<p><%= @heartfelts.enjoyments %><p>

<h4>What are my expected results?</h4>
<p><%= @heartfelts.benefits %></p>

<h4>What kinds of rewards will recieve?</h4>
<p><%= @heartfelts.rewards %></p>

<h4>Do you have a clear mental picture of your goal?</h4>
<% if !@heartfelts.animate.nil? %>
<a href="/animates/<%= @heartfelts.animate.id %>" ><%= @heartfelts.animate.name %></a>
<%end%>
<br>
<br>
<h4>If not, please create one</h4>

<% if @heartfelts.animate.nil?%>
<a href="/animates/new" >Create Mental Picture</a>
<% end %>
<br>
<br>
<h4>Do you wish to update this goal?</h4>
<a href="/heartfelts/<%= @heartfelts.id %>/edit">Edit Here</a>
<br>
<br>
<h4>Do you want to delete this goals?</h4>
<form action="/heartfelts/<%= @heartfelts.id %>" method="POST">
<input type="hidden" name="_method" value="DELETE">
<input type="submit"  id="submit " value="Delete">
</form>
<br>
<a href="/heartfelts">Return to Heartfelt</a><br>




